Which three options are characteristics of N-Port ID Virtualization? (Choose three.)
A. primarily a switch-based technology
B. primarily a host-based solution
C. designed to reduce switch management and overhead in larger SAN deployments
D. introduces a new type of Fibre Channel port, the NP Port, which connects to an F Port

E. introduces a new type of Fibre Channel port, the NP Port, which connects to an F Port
